    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229530/extras/4417679aa0e1428ee534d79ebf0936bd.poster.avif?t=1763328912\" width=948 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229530/extras/4417679aa0e1428ee534d79ebf0936bd.webm?t=1763328912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229530/extras/4417679aa0e1428ee534d79ebf0936bd.mp4?t=1763328912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229530/extras/5930c49c7491c50b7778b8694df990af.poster.avif?t=1763328912\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229530/extras/5930c49c7491c50b7778b8694df990af.webm?t=1763328912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你将见证命运的玩笑，在她随机出现的丑角之一——诺拉身上，一个25岁左右的普通女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道路、车头灯、吱吱作响的车轮、撞击。发生事故后您需要帮助。其中一栋房子的门开着，似乎在邀请人们进来。但与此同时，已经开始的演出大幕也拉开了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细节：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款恐怖游戏，您必须寻找情节对象（钥匙、音符...）、使用手电筒照亮您的路径、使用互动对象（音乐盒、饮料机...）、隐藏并逃离敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您进入视野之前不会注意到您，您可以通过隐藏在转弯处和更衣室来逃脱。这个邪恶超出了你的能力范围，你将无法杀死它，生存并找到出路——这是唯一的解决办法。</p>",
